    <p>If you have multiple content creators on your site, you may want to make their life easier.</p>
<p>One way that you can help is by providing a list of the content they have created.</p>
<p>There are advanced ways to do this, such as using <a href="http://www.ostraining.com/courses/class/drupal/workbench?task=view">the Workbench module</a>, but in this tutorial we'll show you a easy way to provide a list of each user's content.</p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/ostrainingdrupal/~4/U0flJ5y_Xho" height="1" width="1"/>
